channel.title: Looking for 3D modeller
channel.description:
I am working on a 3D game, so I'm looking for a 3D modeller to well, make the 3D models. I can work with 3D modelling programs, but the models I make really suck.
As "payment" I can make you a GM in my game. PM me if you want it.
